data.description: This is such a beautiful home. If you have been looking for a well kept 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home in Hollywood look no further. This home has large tile floors through out. The kitchen has 42 inch cabinets with granite counter tops and stainless steel appliances. This spacious property comes with a bonus room that can be used as a bedroom or family room for entertaining. Roof replaced 5 years ago. The backyard has plenty of room for family gatherings and children to play. Property is located near major shopping centers, highways, entertainment, and beaches. You don't want to miss this property.SELLER IS MOTIVATED. Bring all reasonable offers.
